  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The aim of this study is to compare laparoscopic total extraperitoneal and open mesh repair
      of inguinal hernia, with regard to hospital stay, postoperative pain, quality of life,
      postoperative recovery and return to daily activities, complications and recurrences
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
