  <eligibility>
    <criteria>
      <textblock>
        Inclusion Criteria:

          -  informed consent

          -  age &gt; 18 years

          -  inguinal hernia(primary, recurrence or bilateral)

          -  elective procedure

        Exclusion Criteria:

          -  Scrotal hernia

          -  Prostatectomy, Pfannenstiehl-incision, pre-peritoneal surgery in history

          -  Participation in other trial

          -  Pregnancy

          -  Communicative or cognitive restrictions
      </textblock>
